<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="at-the-same-time">at the same time</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>同时；但：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s impossible to get everybody together at the same time. 
使所有人都同时聚到一起是不可能的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Space travel can be so delightful but at the same time invisibly dangerous. 
太空旅行可以很令人愉快，但同时也存在无形的危险。</p><footer>2015 湖北</footer></div></div>